Frequently Asked Questions

Disney+ is a streaming service where you can watch movies, series, and originals from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, National Geographic, and more.
Access unlimited entertainment with Disney+ Basic or Disney+ Premium in the United States:

  • Disney+ Basic: Disney+ (With Ads) for the price of $9.99/month

  • Disney+ Premium: Disney+ (No Ads*) for the price of $15.99/month or $159.99/year

Save over 16%** on Disney+ Premium (No Ads) with an annual plan for $159.99/year

*Ads will be served in select live and linear content.
**Savings compared to 12 months of the monthly price of Disney+ Premium (No Ads).

Disney+ is the streaming home for entertainment from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, National Geographic, Hulu, ESPN+ and more. With Disney+, you can choose from an always-growing collection of stories.

  • New releases and timeless classics

  • Exclusive new Original Movies and Series

  • A limited selection of hit Hulu series and movies in the Hulu hub on Disney+.

  • Select live sports, studio shows, and more from ESPN+ in the all-new ESPN hub in Disney+

  • Exciting specials and limited-time streaming events

  • Nostalgic throwbacks and past seasons of your favorite shows

  • The entire Skywalker Saga and much of the Marvel Cinematic Universe

  • Beloved and experimental shorts

  • Documentaries, unscripted series, and so much more

The Disney+ app is available on mobile devices, web browsers, game consoles, set-top boxes, and smart TVs. Click to view a complete list of supported devices.

Bundle plans include subscriptions to either Disney+ and Hulu, or Disney+, Hulu, and ESPN+, at discounted prices, as compared to the retail price of each subscription when purchased separately. Available to customers in the United States.

Choose between the following bundle plans:


  • Disney+, Hulu Bundle Basic for $10.99/month, which includes Disney+ (With Ads) and Hulu (With Ads)

  • Disney+, Hulu Bundle Premium for $19.99/month, which includes Disney+ (No Ads*) and Hulu (No Ads*)

  • Disney+, Hulu, ESPN+ Bundle Basic for $16.99/month, which includes Disney+ (With Ads), Hulu (With Ads), and ESPN+ (With Ads) 

  • Disney+, Hulu, ESPN+ Bundle Premium for $26.99/month, which includes Disney+ (No Ads*), Hulu (No Ads*), and ESPN+ (With Ads) 


Additionally, you may also like the following plan offerings:

1. Hulu + Live TV plans

  • Hulu (With Ads) + Live TV, Disney+ (With Ads) and ESPN+ (With Ads) for $82.99/month

  • Hulu (No Ads*) + Live TV, Disney+ (No Ads*) and ESPN+ (With Ads) for $95.99/month

The Hulu + Live TV plans include 95+ live TV channels and additional on-demand content from your favorite sports, entertainment, and news channels you can watch at home or on-the-go. You will also get access to the content from Disney+, Hulu and ESPN+ streaming libraries. Access content from each service separately. Learn more and sign up here.

2. Disney+, Hulu, Max Bundle

Disney+, Hulu, Max Bundle plans include subscriptions to Disney+, Hulu, and Max, at discounted prices, as compared to the monthly retail price of each subscription when purchased separately. Currently, there is no annual subscription for the Disney+, Hulu, Max Bundle.

Choose between the following Disney+, Hulu, Max Bundle Plans:

  • Disney+, Hulu, Max Bundle (With Ads) for $16.99/month, savings of more than $12 per month. This plan includes Disney+, Hulu, and Max all with ads.

  • Disney+, Hulu, Max Bundle (No Ads) for $29.99/month, savings of $21 per month. This plan includes Disney+, Hulu, and Max all without ads. Ads will be served in select live and linear content.

With Disney+, you get new releases, classics, series, and Originals from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, and National Geographic.

With Hulu, you can enjoy current hits, comfort classics, award-winning Originals, and movies like FX’s The Bear and The Kardashians.

With Max, you get access to HBO Originals, Warner Bros. films, the DC universe, and more like Selena + Chef and House of the Dragon.

*Ads will be served in select live and linear content

If you’re a Disney+ subscriber in the United States, you can stream a limited selection of Hulu titles on Disney+. Access the Hulu hub on the Disney+ homepage to preview the Hulu on Disney+ experience.

If you’re a bundle subscriber or you subscribe to both Disney+ and Hulu (as standalone services with the same email address), you can stream a more extensive collection of Hulu titles on Disney+. You can use the Hulu hub on the Disney+ homepage to jump right into streaming some of your favorite Hulu Originals, series, and more. Click to view a list of supported devices.

Eligible Disney+ and Hulu subscribers can watch a wide variety of Hulu’s streaming library on Disney+. Certain Hulu titles are available only via the Hulu app. In addition, the Hulu app will continue to be the streaming destination for Hulu’s entire streaming library, all Hulu premium add-on content as well as any content associated with a Live TV subscription.

Streams is a new feature that carefully curates content from within the Disney+ app or provides access to live linear streams, such as ABC News, to give you a continuous streaming experience. This feature is available for all Disney+ and bundle subscribers. Learn more about what content you can watch with Streams at the Disney+ Help Center.

You can now view a selection of ESPN+ live sports, studio shows, and more in the all-new ESPN hub of your Disney+ app.

Available to all Disney+ and Bundle subscribers, ESPN on Disney+ has something for everyone, depending on your subscription:

  • If you have an ESPN+ subscription (either as part of a bundle that includes ESPN+ or a standalone ESPN+ subscription in addition to your Disney+ subscription), you’ll access all of ESPN+ – including thousands of live sports from top leagues including the NFL, NHL, UFC, PGA TOUR, LALIGA, and college sports, and ESPN Original films and the full 30 for 30 library – directly in Disney+. Does not include Pay-Per-View events or other add-ons, which you must purchase and watch directly in the ESPN app.

  • If you don’t have an ESPN+ subscription, you will still receive a curated selection of ESPN+ content for no additional cost. Stream a curated selection of ESPN+ live events from top leagues including the NHL, and ESPN Originals and studio shows, right on Disney+. Learn more.

Find your ESPN+ titles in your Disney+ homepage, in the ESPN hub, and through Search.

ESPN+ content includes many sports programs that do not have ratings, including live events, news, and more. These programs may include content and advertising* that may feature mature themes, products, and services, like you would typically see on a regular television broadcast.

  • These programs will be available to all profiles on your Disney+ account (except for Junior Mode profiles). You can control access to these programs for each profile using our parental control settings. Learn more.

  • Programs and titles outside these categories (for example, programs with content ratings and certain on-demand titles without content ratings) will continue to adhere to the content ratings and maturity settings of each profile.

*Ads will be served in select live and linear content for all Disney+ plans. Titles without ratings like live sports, news, and more, and the advertisements included therein, may feature mature themes, products, and services.
